column2: Create a shock wave that bleeds and cripples nearby foes.

The Flame headquarters seemed impenetrable, until your solo incursion proved we do have a chance. Your inspiration in showing us what is possible was a welcome shot in the arm. You did excellent work, %str1%.

Thank you again.

— Remaris Earshot

Your invaluable contribution toward the mill's upkeep have made it possible for us to be up and running again. 

Thank you again for helping out.

— Mara Ripsaw
Reflect projectiles while damaging nearby foes.

Throw your shield in a line, crippling struck foes. This attack deals bonus damage if you have barrier.

Bryllana and the Iron Legion thank you for your service. Well done!
Bravo! The Ash Legion have made progress against the ghosts in Victor's Presidium.
Protect the fisher folk from the drakes, clean up tar, and fix broken traps around Lake Feritas.
Strum Bassclash is impressed. You helped secure Lake Feritas.
The wrecking yard is more organized. Scar Stripeclaw thanks you.
Latera Painstorm is impressed. You helped punish the Flame Legion.
Double-click to apply this look to any other heavy helmet.
The Iron Legion appreciates your help fighting the Flame Legion.
The Blood Legion salutes you, soldier. Impressive work!
Double-click to apply this look to any other heavy leggings.
The troops are training hard, thanks to you.
Kill Separatists, destroy their mines, disrupt their plans, and rescue captured charr.
The Separatists won't soon forget your name. You've done a service for the charr.
The Iron Legion thanks you for your help!
Double-click to apply this look to any other heavy shoulders.
Excellent! You've helped make valuable research possible!
Wipe out the ghosts haunting Ascalon City and help the Blood Legion retake the city for the charr.
You've shown true fortitude against the ghosts!
